AUDIO: 'to modify the splat they get. And that is there are lots of layers to that. Today we are going deep on a new [music] approach to 3D capture that could fundamentally change how products are sold online. I\'m joined by Mariam Ferat, co-founder and CEO of Solaya, a deep'

[00:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
